\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 It appeared there was no way around it. Marcus accepted the inevitable, sat his naked ass down on the cool tile, crossed his legs in a fashion resembling a relaxed lotus position, and closed his eyes. He began focusing on his breathing, starting through the breathing exercises he used to cope with pain, just in case. Depending on just how strenuous this was, this could very well be akin to torture. No matter how intense it was, or wasn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t for that matter, he was pretty sure this was going to be a world of suck for a while.}}